        ## Installation
        
        See https://ciecplib.readthedocs.io/en/latest/#installation for installation instructions.
        
        ## Basic usage
        
        ```python
        >>> from ciecplib import request
        >>> response = request('https://somewhere.org/mywebpage/')
        ```
        
